FoundrList is a modern startup discovery platform that helps founders, creators, indie hackers, and SaaS builders gain visibility. List your startup, explore new projects, and connect with makers building the future inside a trusted founder community .

Built with Next.js for blazing-fast performance and Supabase for reliable, scalable real-time data, FoundrList provides a powerful ecosystem for showcasing innovation. Whether you're launching a SaaS, building an app, or creating indie products, FoundrList helps you reach users, investors, and global audiences.

This startup directory and startup listing website is optimized to rank for searches like startup discovery platform , where to list my startup , and discover SaaS products . Clean metadata, OG tags, and canonical URLs make every listing crawlable and sharable.

  • Startup directory with instant, SEO-friendly listings

  • Founder showcase pages with OG images and keywords
  • Next.js SEO architecture tuned for Core Web Vitals
  • Supabase real-time data powering votes and comments
  • Responsive, mobile-first design that stays fast and accessible

SEO-friendly slugs, structured data, and a curated startup marketplace keep launches visible. From Next.js Supabase SaaS project examples to founder showcase pages, every detail supports organic discovery and community momentum.
